    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="mysql时区问题"><a href="#mysql时区问题" class="headerlink" title="mysql时区问题"></a>mysql时区问题</h2><p>参考：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ZYC88888/article/details/86597674" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mysql时区问题解决几种方法_数据库_赵英超的博客-CSDN博客</a></p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">set global time_zone = '+8:00';  ##修改mysql全局时区为北京时间，即我们所在的东8区</span><br><span class="line">set time_zone = '+8:00';  ##修改当前会话时区</span><br><span class="line">flush privileges;  #立即生效</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 增加参数</span></span><br><span class="line">jdbc.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/demo?characterEncoding=UTF-8&amp;useSSL=false&amp;serverTimezone=Asia/Shanghai</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
